Eating Contest Party
Dustin went
This will be an event at our house with various eating contests (plus regular food), like: - Saltine Challenge - Taco-stravaganza: http://ywong.livejournal.com/292882.html - Funny Bunny - Pie-Eating Contest - CinnaMunch Showdown - Cheese-Puff Catching - .... more? (Original note: http://www.facebook.com/note.php?note_id=92502136831&comments ) Not everyone who attends has to participate, but non-contestants are encouraged to pledge donations to offset the food outlay. If there are enough pledges, we will award prizes too. You can also pledge money - PayPal me - if you are not coming, and we will make sure to photo/video-document whatever event(s) you want to see and post them on Facebook! If anyone has ideas for other contests, please post them in the comments! When RSVP'ing, please indicate which contest(s) you are willing to enter. We will also invite James Wang to be on hand in case anything goes wrong. Guests are welcome! Please share this event with others, especially those whom you think would be particularly good/hilarious at an eating contest!
